This message from women's NGOs and health care providers helped both my client and her fiance become strong and committed 21st century men, willing to sacrifice their "rights" for the sake of their family. Several months after #2, my client paid her older daughter's surgery, and all our family contributed financially for #2's delivery. As you can imagine, my friends and my client's family are very happy with the positive choices she has made and her ability to have a loving relationship with my family.

Thank you again for your help in making this a developmental success story. It is a rare event these days, and our families celebrate it together!
